				<h1 class="name post-title entry-title" itemprop="name">Top 5 Yom Kippur War Movies Recommended by Steven Spielberg</h1>
						
<p class="post-meta">
		
	<span>Posted by: <a href="http://www.breakingisraelnews.com/author/breakingisraelnews/" title="">Staff Writer </a></span>
	
		
	<span>September 13, 2013 , 12:04 pm</span>	
	
</p>
<div class="clear"></div>
	

